thread.title: John Van

author: John Van
title: John Van
text:
Servcorp offers a convenient and cost effective virtual office for start up small businesses like myself who are a one man show but has the secretarial support like a real office. It offers flexibility to be in an out of your main location as well as other main centres makes it convenient to meet clients anywhere.
The staff to management are always open and willing to help and make life easy for us to do our business better. I am very happy and thank you for all the support that the team at Servcorp in Parramatta that has made my life easier and grow my business.
